<h1>Add Instructor </h1>
<p>On this page you will be able to add a user (who is already authorized as an instructor on this platform) as an instructor for the running simulation being worked on. </p>
<p>The new instructor will be able to add and remove students, send email and do any thing else that can be accessed from this facilitation section of the software.</p>
<p>But please note, adding someone as an instructor does not automatically give them player access to  the simulation. For that to happen, they will need to be assinged a role in the simulation. </p>
